Episode 2940:
----------------------
Popatlal tries to make fried snacks for the breakfast but he notices that he does not have any tomato sauce in the house to have with the snacks. So, he tries to call Abdul, but Abdul does not pick his phone up. Popatlal then comes out in the balcony of his house and shouts Abdul‚Äôs name. Bhide and others notice Popatlal shouting so they ask him the reason for his yelling. Popatlal tells everyone that he has made some fried snacks and he needs some tomato sauce to eat with it. Bhide tells Popatlal that he will give him the tomato sauce. Later, Bhide goes to Popatlal with a bottle of tomato sauce and leaves. When Popatlal notices that the tomato is expired he comes downstairs screaming Bhide‚Äôs name. What will Popatlal do now? Let‚Äôs find out.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant.The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

snippet.title: We are taking a break ! Leaving Saudi Arabia ! Cargo Packing !
snippet.description:
This video might be a surprise for most of you. Yes, we are leaving Saudi Arabia and moving back to our homeland, Kerala. Lots of plans and there‚Äôs more surprises coming up. Will let you know soon. Till then stay tuned and do watch this video of few moments taken here and there. Few shopping, few me-time moments, few family time and so on. 

Saudi Arabia is a country where I found myself. I got an identity from here and will always be thankful for the warmth and shelter this country had provided us. Initially it was tough, but  gradually became in love with this beautiful land.

We badly needed a break from all the stress revolving around. Really happy and positive with the decision, to spend sometime with our family back in Kerala. 

We had to shift many stuff, specially crockeries. We approached a team with very reasonable rate. If you are in Saudi Arabia and looking forward for sea cargo, Please contact the below person.

snippet.title: Major Beginnings | 'The Look' Test | Adivi Sesh | Sashi Kiran Tikka | Major The Film
snippet.description:
‚ÄòThe film speaks about the way he lived, not about the way he lost life.‚Äô 
November 27 is not just a remembrance day, but the day to celebrate Major #SandeepUnnikrishnan's life. We share this video in honour of the man who has instilled pride in a billion hearts.
#MajorTheFilm #MajorBeginnings

Based on the life of real-life Hero Major Sandeep Unnikrishnan, Major, the film, aims to show how this valiant soldier saved the lives of numerous hostages before being martyred by the activists who wreaked havoc in the Taj Mahal Palace Mumbai, India on the 26th of November, 2008.

Major, a bilingual Hindi and Telugu film has been produced by Sony Pictures Films India in association with Mahesh Babu's GMB Entertainment Pvt. Ltd. and A+S Movies. It is directed by acclaimed Telugu director Sashi Kiran Tikka and features Adivi Sesh, Sobhita Dhulipala and Saiee Manjrekar.

snippet.title: Remembering Diego Maradona: football legend dies aged 60
snippet.description:
Diego Maradona, widely regarded as one of the greatest football players of all time, has died at the age of 60. Maradona was a uniquely gifted player with a bewitching style that was all his own. He rose from the streets of Buenos Aires to reach the pinnacle of his sport leading Argentina to World Cup glory in 1986 and scoring the infamous 'Hand of God' goal along the way. Maradona played for Boca Juniors, Barcelona and Napoli in a storied club career, and later managed Argentina at the 2010 World Cup.

Declaring three days of national mourning, Alberto Fern√°ndez, the president of Argentina, said: 'You took us to the top of the world. You made us immensely happy. You were the greatest of them all'.

snippet.title: Olive and Mabel - still taking a paws.
snippet.description:
Really just wanted to say thank you for all the nice comments on all the videos. And sorry for a lack of new ones (which will come). Too much time being taken up by the book and I feel distinctly uncomfortable doing the shameless business of trying to promote it. But then, a whole lot of work went in to it and the best I can do is say that lots of people who have enjoyed the videos have also enjoyed the book. 'Olive, Mabel & Me' coming out in the USA and Canada on 1st December and already out elsewhere. 
Audiobook version coming soon.
Be careful out there...

snippet.title: Remembering Diego Maradona: football legend dies aged 60
snippet.description:
Diego Maradona, widely regarded as one of the greatest football players of all time, has died at the age of 60. Maradona was a uniquely gifted player with a bewitching style that was all his own. He rose from the streets of Buenos Aires to reach the pinnacle of his sport leading Argentina to World Cup glory in 1986 and scoring the infamous 'Hand of God' goal along the way. Maradona played for Boca Juniors, Barcelona and Napoli in a storied club career, and later managed Argentina at the 2010 World Cup.

Declaring three days of national mourning, Alberto Fern√°ndez, the president of Argentina, said: 'You took us to the top of the world. You made us immensely happy. You were the greatest of them all'.

0:00 - Intro

11:30 - Criteria for potential life partner 
14:46 - Comments from family

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Leeds vs Arsenal (0-0) | Premier League
snippet.description:
Nicolas Pepe was sent off for the first time in his career but we stood firm to secure a point at Elland Road.

The Ivory Coast winger saw red early in the second half following an off-the-ball clash with Ezgjan Alioski.

We were forced back after that but stout defending, the woodwork and fine goalkeeping from Bernd Leno kept Leeds at bay.

And we almost snatched victory when Bukayo Saka raced through to force a save from Illan Meslier.

An attacking reshuffle saw Willian and Pepe both start, and we were collectively bright and tenacious in the early stages.

Pepe inadvertently hit the crossbar with an attempted cross from the left, and Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang slashed a shot high and wide on the turn after excellent work from Hector Bellerin.

Leeds goalkeeper Meslier wasn't tested, but Leno was. He had to save from Patrick Bamford - twice - and chances also came and went for Raphinha, Stuart Dallas and Mateus Klick as Leeds started to get on top.

Mikel Arteta brought on Reiss Nelson at half-time but our gameplan was undermined when Pepe was sent off by Anthony Taylor once the referee had checked footage of his altercation with Alioski.

Leno made a wonderful one-handed save to keep out a Dallas shot that was headed for the top corner, and substitute Rodrigo crashed a shot off the crossbar.

We looked set for a Leeds siege but, instead, we opened up the home side on the break.

One charge ended with an Aubameyang shot that was blocked by Liam Cooper's arm as the defender slid in. On this occasion, VAR was not called upon.

Saka raced through moments later but Meslier stood his ground to block the England international's shot.

Bamford headed against the post and Raphinha hit the bar as Leeds continued to threaten - but we kept a valuable clean sheet.

#arsenal #premierleague #leedsunited

snippet.title: Remembering Diego Maradona: football legend dies aged 60
snippet.description:
Diego Maradona, widely regarded as one of the greatest football players of all time, has died at the age of 60. Maradona was a uniquely gifted player with a bewitching style that was all his own. He rose from the streets of Buenos Aires to reach the pinnacle of his sport leading Argentina to World Cup glory in 1986 and scoring the infamous 'Hand of God' goal along the way. Maradona played for Boca Juniors, Barcelona and Napoli in a storied club career, and later managed Argentina at the 2010 World Cup.

Declaring three days of national mourning, Alberto Fern√°ndez, the president of Argentina, said: 'You took us to the top of the world. You made us immensely happy. You were the greatest of them all'.

snippet.localized.title: Remembering Diego Maradona: football legend dies aged 60
snippet.localized.description:
Diego Maradona, widely regarded as one of the greatest football players of all time, has died at the age of 60. Maradona was a uniquely gifted player with a bewitching style that was all his own. He rose from the streets of Buenos Aires to reach the pinnacle of his sport leading Argentina to World Cup glory in 1986 and scoring the infamous 'Hand of God' goal along the way. Maradona played for Boca Juniors, Barcelona and Napoli in a storied club career, and later managed Argentina at the 2010 World Cup.

Declaring three days of national mourning, Alberto Fern√°ndez, the president of Argentina, said: 'You took us to the top of the world. You made us immensely happy. You were the greatest of them all'.

snippet.title: Aku Bidadari Syurgamu - Aishah | #SFMM35
snippet.description:
Antara acara yang dinanti-nantikan saban tahun terutamanya buat peminat serta penggiat seni muzik tanah air. Di sinilah pentas penentuan untuk 30 lagu yang telah berjaya mara ke pusingan Muzik Muzik 35 Separuh Akhir dalam perjuangan tahunan ke acara kemuncak Anugerah Juara Lagu.

Lagu manakah yang akan layak ke AJL 35? Nantikan siaran langsung Muzik Muzik 35 Separuh Akhir (SFMM35) di saluran YouTube TV3Malaysia yang akan diadakan selama 3 hari berturut-turut bermula 20 November (Jumaat) sehingga 22 November (Ahad) pada jam 9 malam.

Berikut lagu-lagu yang akan dipertandingkan:

1. Sakit - Zynakal & Yonnyboii
Komposer & Lirik: Yonnyboii & Zynakal

2. Sembah - Naim Daniel ft Man Keedal
Komposer & Lirik: Naim Daniel & Iqie Hugh

3. Panggung - Apex Tajudin
Komposer & Lirik: Faizal Tahir, Mage, Mike Chan, Karim Karam & Romeo

4. Kau Sakiti - Amir Masdi
Komposer & Lirik: Faizal Tahir, Mike Chan, Ezra Kong, Romeo & Mage

5. Tentang Rahsia - Judika & Shila Amzah
Komposer: Farouk Roman
Lirik: Amylea

6. Bicara Rasa - Ariff Bahran & Sarah Suhairi
Komposer & Lirik: Rudy Kasmaran & Sang Hitam

7. Takdir Tercipta - Hafiz Suip & Adira
Komposer: Ikhwan Fatanna & Ayden Ali
Lirik: Ikhwan Fatanna & Arisz Ab Rahman

8. 7 Nasihat - Dato‚Äô Sri Siti Nurhaliza, Kmy Kmo & Luca Sickta
Komposer & Lirik: Kmy Kmo & Luca Sickta

9. Hutang - Floor 88
Komposer: Zai Hamzah
Lirik: Achoi Floor 88

10. Aku Bidadari Syurgamu - Dato‚Äô Sri Siti Nurhaliza
Komposer: Ippo Hafiz
Lirik: Siti Rosmizah

60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen‚Äôs weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast‚Äôs segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program‚Äôs executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O‚ÄôDonnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Cyberpunk 2077 ‚Äî Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In this world, consumed by neverending conflict, sometimes only an outsider will get the job done. And that's you.

Cyberpunk 2077, an open-world, action-adventure story from CD PROJEKT RED, is coming to Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PC, and Google Stadia on December 10th, 2020. The game will also be playable on Xbox Series X and PlayStation 5 consoles when available.

Pre-order now: https://www.cyberpunk.net/pre-order

About the game:
Cyberpunk 2077 is an open-world, action-adventure story set in Night City, a megalopolis obsessed with power, glamour and body modification. You play as V, a mercenary outlaw going after a one-of-a-kind implant that is the key to immortality. You can customize your character‚Äôs cyberware, skillset and playstyle, and explore a vast city where the choices you make shape the story and the world around you.

Learn more:
https://www.cyberpunk.net 
https://www.twitter.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.facebook.com/CyberpunkGame 
https://www.instagram.com/CyberpunkGame
https://www.discord.gg/CyberpunkGame
https://www.CyberpunkGame.tumblr.com

Tracks:

Title: Come Close
Created by: Sebastian Robertson and Daniel Davies

Title: Suicide
Created by: Geno Lenardo feat. Valin "ZEALE" Zamerron

Title: Makes Me Feel Better
Created by: Kevin Hastings

snippet.description:
Get tickets for Dua Lipa's Studio 2054 üëâüèº  https://dualipa.co/Studio2054-General... üëàüèº  a kaleidoscopic rocket fuelled journey through time, space, mirror-balls, roller discos, bucket hats, belting beats, throbbing bass-lines and an absolute slam dunk of the best times in global club culture throughout the decades.

Taken from her second studio album 'Future Nostalgia' released in 2020, which featured the hit singles 'Don't Start Now', 'Physical', 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' & 'Levitating'

Get the album Future Nostalgia : https://dualipa.co/futurenostalgia

Twitter: http://dualipa.co/twitter
YouTube: https://dualipa.co/youtube

About Dua Lipa:
Born and raised in London to Kosovar-Albanian parents Dua Lipa signed to Warner Records in 2015, releasing her self titled debut in 2017 which featured the hit singles, 'Be The One', 'IDGAF', 'Hotter Than Hell' & her first UK #1 hit 'New Rules'. 

Critical success soon followed as Dua Lipa picked up Brit Awards for 'Best Female Solo Artist' and 'Best British Breakthrough Act' as well as Grammy Awards for 'Best New Artist' and 'Best Dance Recording' for the track 'Electricity' in collaboration with Silk City.

Her second internationally acclaimed studio album 'Future Nostalgia' was released in 2020 and included the hit singles 'Don't Start Now, 'Break My Heart', 'Hallucinate' and 'Levitating', with the remix album 'Club Future Nostalgia' following shortly after featuring guest appearances from 'Blackpink', 'Missy Elliott', 'Madonna' and 'Gwen Stefani'. 

#DuaLipa #Levitating #FutureNostalgia

snippet.title: Indoo Ki Jawani Official Trailer | Kiara Advani, Aditya Seal, Mallika Dua, Abir Sengupta | 11 Dec
snippet.description:
Gulshan Kumar, T-Series Films In Association With Emmay Entertainment, Electric Apples Entertainment, An Emmay Entertainment Production presents the trailer of upcoming Bollywood movie "INDOO KI JAWANI" written & directed by Abir Sengupta and produced by Bhushan Kumar, Divya Khosla Kumar, Krishan Kumar, Monisha Advani, Madhu Bhojwani, Nikkhil Advani, Ryan Stephen, Niranjan Iyengar. snippet.title: Corona-Regeln f√ºr Dezember | Pressekonferenz mit Merkel, M√ºller und S√∂der
snippet.description:
Im Kampf gegen die Corona-Pandemie haben sich Bund und L√§nder auf weitere Einschr√§nkungen geeinigt. Der Lockdown-light mit geschlossenen Gastronomie-, Freizeit- und Kultureinrichtungen wird bis 20. Dezember verl√§ngert. Bundeskanzlerin Merkel sagte nach den Beratungen, dass die Ma√ünahmen voraussichtlich noch bis Anfang Januar gelten werden.

https://www.tagesschau.de/inland/bund-laender-corona-111.html

Es sei notwendig, die Kontakte weiter zu reduzieren, deswegen habe man sich auf weitere Einschr√§nkungen verst√§ndigt. Es komme weiterhin auf jeden und jede Einzelne an. Merkel mahnte zu Geduld, Solidarit√§t und Disziplin.

Die Kontaktauflagen werden weiter versch√§rft: Private Zusammenk√ºnfte m√ºssen auf den eigenen und einen weiteren Haushalt beschr√§nkt werden - maximal f√ºnf Personen sind dann erlaubt. Kinder bis 14 Jahre werden von der Regel ausgenommen.

F√ºr die Weihnachtstage und Silvester sollen diese Regeln gelockert werden. Vom 23. Dezember an sollen Treffen "im engsten Familien- oder Freundeskreis" m√∂glich sein, und zwar bis maximal zehn Personen insgesamt. Dazugeh√∂rige Kinder bis 14 Jahre sollen hiervon ausgenommen sein. Die Ausnahmeregelung soll "l√§ngstens" bis zum 1. Januar gelten.

F√ºr den Einzelhandel werden die Ma√ünahmen versch√§rft. In kleineren L√§den soll sich nur ein Kunde pro zehn Quadratmetern aufhalten d√ºrfen, in gr√∂√üeren Gesch√§ften sind es 20 Quadratmeter pro Person.

In den Schulen soll ab der achten Klassenstufe auf Hybrid- und Wechselunterricht gesetzt werden. In besonders stark betroffenen Corona-Hotspots wird es noch restriktivere Ma√ünahmen als bisher geben.

Nach Angaben der Kanzlerin haben Bund und L√§nder eine dritte Schwelle bei den Sieben-Tages-Inzidenzen eingezogen. Bei mehr als 200 Neuinfektionen pro 100.000 Einwohnern binnen sieben Tagen m√ºssten noch einmal sch√§rfere Einschr√§nkungen verh√§ngt werden. Dies betreffe zurzeit ganz Berlin sowie 62 Landkreise in Deutschland.

Die Bundesl√§nder k√∂nnen nach den Beschl√ºssen des Corona-Gipfels k√ºnftig abh√§ngig von der Infektionslage entscheiden, ob sie Ma√ünahmen lockern oder versch√§rfen. Berlins Regierender B√ºrgermeister Michael M√ºller (SPD) sagte im Anschluss an die Gespr√§che, Bundesl√§nder mit sehr guten Zahlen h√§tten jetzt die M√∂glichkeit zur Erleichterung. Gleichzeitig seien L√§nder mit sehr hohen Infektionszahlen in der Pflicht, sich damit auseinanderzusetzen und m√∂gliche Versch√§rfungen zu pr√ºfen.

snippet.title: "Lockdown bis M√§rz?" - Lindner attackiert Coronapolitik der Bundesregierung
snippet.description:
Der FDP-Fraktionsvorsitzende Christian Lindner hat der Bundesregierung am Donnerstag im Bundestag kein gutes Zeugnis f√ºr ihre Corona-Politik und -Ma√ünahmen ausstellen wollen. Vor allem kritisierte er die Lockdown-Politik, die zun√§chst nur f√ºr November gelten sollte, nach einem erneuten L√§nder-Regierungs-Gipfel am Mittwoch aber bis Januar. Und am n√§chsten Tag spreche der Kanzleramtsminister Helge Braun schon davon, dass der Stillstand bis M√§rz zu gehen drohe. Die Herangehensweise, Ma√ünahmen f√ºr alle zu verh√§ngen, sei wenig zielf√ºhrend und nicht durchhaltbar aus wirtschaftlicher Sicht. Sie drohe laut Lindner, die Innenst√§dte ver√∂den zu lassen, Amazon noch mehr Marktanteile zuzuspielen, ohne dabei wirklich gegen die Pandemie hilfreich zu sein. Um die Coronama√ünahmen effektiv zu gestalten, m√ºsse man einen Schutzschirm f√ºr vulnerable Gruppen errichten, anstatt auf Schulden und Verbote zu setzen.

Unsinnig an den f√ºr Dezember verh√§ngten Ma√ünahmen sei auch, dass Menschen weiterhin eng in √∂ffentlichen Verkehrsmitteln beieinander sitzen und in Schlangen vor Gesch√§ften stehen d√ºrfen, um dann im Gesch√§ft 20 Quadratmeter f√ºr sich zugesprochen zu bekommen.

snippet.title: B√∂hse Onkelz - Waldstadion Live in Frankfurt 2018 (Teaser)
snippet.description:
Ihr habt es vielfach gew√ºnscht, wir denken dass es genau zur richtigen Zeit kommt, um euch √ºber Corona, Quarant√§ne und den Winter die Zeit zu vertreiben: Live in Frankfurt 2018.

Vom Fahnenmeer, den der B.O.S.C. organisierte, bis zum euphorischen Schlussakkord eines magischen Abends, den wir nie vergessen werden.
Unser erstes Mal im Waldstadion. IM WALDSTADION!
60.000 Neffen und Nichten, wo sonst die SGE spielt und angefeuert wird.

Zum Erinnern und f√ºrs immer wieder gucken nun das ganze Set. Fast drei Stunden der ganze uns aufw√ºhlende, emotionale Wahnsinn auf 2 DVDs oder 1 Blu-ray. Nicht viel Brimborium, fast schon ein bisschen bootlegm√§ssig, aber in Sound, Gef√ºhl und Bild √ºberw√§ltigend.

Ab 11. Dezember.

Eure Onkelz

Schluss machen mit der eigenen Familie ‚Äì und das von einem auf den anderen Tag.¬†H√§ufig sch√§men sich die Betroffenen f√ºr einen pl√∂tzlichen Kontaktabbruch zur eigenen Familie oder von Familienmitgliedern. Die wenigsten trauen sich, offen dar√ºber zu sprechen.
Wie oft es zu einem Kontaktabbruch innerhalb der Familie kommt, ist nicht erfasst:
Es gibt keine Studien oder Zahlen dar√ºber, wieviele Menschen in Deutschland sich von ihrer Familie getrennt haben. Viele Betroffene berichten jedoch in verschiedenen Foren und Selbsthilfegruppen √ºber ihre Situation und dem erlittenen Verlust. 
Reporterin Alexa Ramthun will erfahren, wieso Menschen den Kontakt zu ihren Eltern abbrechen, ohne den Grund zu nennen und wie es sich anf√ºhlt, wenn das eigene Kind keinen Kontakt mehr will. 
Protagonistin Anne hat sich vor f√ºnf Jahren von ihrer Familie getrennt und lebt seitdem ein scheinbar gl√ºckliches Leben mit ihrem Freund, ihrem Hund und ihren engsten Freunden. Ein kl√§rendes Gespr√§ch mit ihren Eltern gab es nie. Sie haben nie erfahren, aus welchen Gr√ºnden  Anne ihre Familie verlassen hat. 
Martina steht dagegen auf der anderen Seite: ihre Tochter hat vor elf Jahren den Kontakt zu ihr abgebrochen, sie kann sich bis heute nicht erkl√§ren, wieso. Um den Schmerz, die Hilflosigkeit und die Ungewissheit irgendwie verarbeiten zu k√∂nnen, besucht sie unter anderem regelm√§√üig eine Selbsthilfegruppe. Reporterin Alexa darf bei einer Sitzung dabei sein und bekommt einen Einblick, wie es in einer solchen Gruppe abl√§uft. 
Wie gehen verlassene Eltern mit diesem Verlustgef√ºhl um? L√§sst der Schmerz irgendwann nach? Und geht es Menschen, die ihre Familie verlassen haben, tats√§chlich besser?
